Once opon a time in a forest there lived a monkey who resided on a jamun tree which was on the bank of the river.
In the same forest there lived a crocodile and his wife.
On day the crocodile came to the bank's of the river and rested under the kind herted monkey offered him some fruits the crocodile came back the next day for more fruits as he love them. As day passed by the crocodile and monkey become good friends. One day a monkey sent some fruits for crocodile's wife.She ate the fruits and loved them but was jeoulous as she did not like her husband spending time with the monkey.She told het husband that if the fruits are so juicy then I wonder how sweet the monley's heart would be? Get me the heart of monkey.The crocodile was not willing to kill but he had no choice.
